Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:04.28,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Până aici mi-a fost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:07.43,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Vă rog să... continuați fără...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:13.92,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:14.99,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.14,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Nu în căruță! Nu în căruță!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.77,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Oare va fi în regulă?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:23.54,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Păi, nu e ceva nou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:27.13,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Totuși, are un teribil rău de mișcare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.82,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Nu mai rezist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:30.80,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Oh, domnule!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.25,main,Horn,0,0,0,,O putem vedea acum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.01,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Aceea e capitala regală,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.11,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Seven Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.10,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Ce treburi aveți aici?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.56,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Un bărbat dubios cu coarne?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.37,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Nu ești o creatură demonică, nu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:49.57,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Oh, haide, ne-au înconjurat deja?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:53.32,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Lumachina e cu noi, \Ndeci nu vreau să provoc zarvă.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.32,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Hei, tu, femeia de acolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.32,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Dă-ți jos gluga ca să-ți putea vedea fața!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.70,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Se pare că nu am de ales. \NÎi voi intimida puțin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:09.06,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Presupun că sunteți pregătiți de consecințe din moment ce îndreptați sulițele spre mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.84,main,Soldier,0,0,0,,N-Nemernicule...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.30,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Diablo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.02,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Nu mai există cale de întoarcere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.47,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Se pare că trebuie să continui cu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.85,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Vă rog să așteptați.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.98,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Ați putea lăsa aceste persoane să treacă?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.21,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Tu ești...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.72,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Nu ne-am văzut de mult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:37.53,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Am primit scrisoarea lui Rem și te așteptam, Diablo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.19,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Alicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.25,sign_5613_32_Episode_1__Head_,Screen,0,0,0,,Episodul 8: Vizită în capitala regală
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.60,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Incredibil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.46,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Poți vedea întreaga capitală de aici!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.96,main,Horn,0,0,0,,E uimitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:22.68,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Vă rog să folosiți acest han după cum doriți, \Npe timpul șederii voastre în capitală.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:27.18,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Ei bine, Alicia, îți apreciem amabilitatea...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.91,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Dar dacă vom sta într-un asemenea loc, vom rămâne fără bani cât ai zice pește.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.02,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Nu trebuie să vă faceți griji de asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.56,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Doar lăsați totul în seama mea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.04,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Ce? În acest caz...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:37.98,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.90,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Dacă Diablo îmi cere, voi cumpăra acest han cât ai bate din palme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.59,main,Rem,0,0,0,,C-Ce... tocmai... a spus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.33,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.65,main,Daiblo,0,0,0,,Hm... Bine spus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:51.91,italics,Daiblo,0,0,0,,La naiba! Cât de bogată e Alicia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.34,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,I apologize for the delayed \Nintroduction, Head Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:00.35,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Alicia Cristela, un cavaler regal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.80,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,E o onoare să te întâlnesc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.80,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumim pentru că ne-ai ajutat să intrăm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.17,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Mă bucur că am putut fi de ajutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.64,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Scuză-mă, dar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.28,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Ce relație ai cu stăpânul meu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.98,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:21.44,main,Rose,0,0,0,,My entire being exists to serve my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.02,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Sh-Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.36,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Alicia is a Demon Lord worshiper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.83,italics,,0,0,0,,who put our lives in danger \Nto resurrect the Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:33.75,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Even though she's sworn loyalty to \Nme now, if Rose learns about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.31,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Rose, you don't need to pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.47,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,If he asked me to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.66,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,If he asked me to die, then I would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.92,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Does that explanation suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:50.10,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Then it would be correct to recognize \Nyou as one of my master's possessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.94,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Unless he has forsaken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.32,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:01.11,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Then I shall I recognize you \Nas one of Master's possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.40,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.99,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,And you must be Horn-san, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.99,top,Alicia,0,0,0,,I heard you recently joined his companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.36,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She got past Rose so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.13,top,Horn,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.79,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Her communication skills are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.16,main,Shera,0,0,0,,I can't go on any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.58,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.32,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Thank you... for everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.84,main,Horn,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.20,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I can't eat any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.46,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.47,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.76,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Even my healing can't help with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:37.19,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I wanted to eat a lot so I can become big and\Nstrong like you, Mister, and help out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.69,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Grasswalkers will always look like children,\N even after reaching adulthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.01,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I know that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:47.52,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Well, just take your time \Nand serve me faithfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.65,main,Rose,0,0,0,,If my master desires it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:53.12,main,Rose,0,0,0,,then as much as I wouldn't like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.24,main,Rose,0,0,0,,there is a way to empower her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.53,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Empower me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.79,main,Rose,0,0,0,,If you place this treasure around your neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.52,main,Rose,0,0,0,,it will form a Master-Servant Pact\N with my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.05,main,Rose,0,0,0,,and the Servant's abilities \Nwill be empowered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.48,main,Horn,0,0,0,,A Master-Servant Pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.80,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.19,main,Horn,0,0,0,,A pact with him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.64,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:21.54,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Doesn't the servant who forges that \Npact die when the master does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.25,top,Diablo,0,0,0,,Please let me go to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.23,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I-I'll die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.40,main,Rose,0,0,0,,What's the problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.49,main,Rose,0,0,0,,My master possesses unparalleled power,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.49,main,Rose,0,0,0,,so becoming his servant would grant \Nmore benefits than words can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.88,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I'd become that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.45,main,Horn,0,0,0,,But I'd die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.63,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.21,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Once you forge that pact, \Nthere's no way to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.54,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Also, how will you go about finding work
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.51,main,Rem,0,0,0,,or someone to marry you in the future \Nif you have a collar around your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.43,main,Rem,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.18,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.19,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.00,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.59,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:14.74,main,Rose,0,0,0,,The idea of letting riffraff get close \Nto my master is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.58,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,I've arranged sleeping \Nchambers for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.68,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,It might be a little cramped \Nfor you, Diablo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.76,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.54,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,No, it won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:28.10,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,This is practically a king's bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.84,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,So it seems you've already \Nsurmised the general situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.84,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.33,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Diablo-sama, might I draw closer to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.94,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.06,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.29,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.50,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She's getting this close?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.80,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,You've come to the royal capital \Nbecause of Lumachina-sama, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.34,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:56.07,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,The king hasn't learned that \NI plotted to resurrect the Demon Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.83,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,but I was held responsible for \Nmy absence during the emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.33,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,so I'm currently under confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:06.14,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,But I believe I can prove \Nuseful to you, Diablo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.92,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Please tell me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.30,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She's a virgin killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.57,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She manages to look innocent \Ninstead of slutty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.66,italics,,0,0,0,,while making such a strong appeal \Nwith her feminine features!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.32,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She's a true virgin killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.81,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Alicia is to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.31,main,Rem,0,0,0,,What's the matter, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.15,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Uh, the room was too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.82,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't relax in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.48,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Want to sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:32.57,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.78,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,So the Head Cardinal, Vishos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:40.43,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,He sought Lumachina-sama's life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.72,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,The mortal races truly are disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.18,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Even the Church that believes in God...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.46,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Naturally, we'll need to make \Nthem pay for their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.48,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:53.60,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,I can gather evidence of their wrongdoing,\Nas you've requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.68,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:57.64,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,It's unlikely we can make \Nthem answer for their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.60,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:03.52,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,The kingdom is unable to interfere \Nin the Church's internal affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.34,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,So it won't be able to sentence \NVishos and the other Cardinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:15.03,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,This is why we need your power, Diablo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:15.86,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.99,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Enact a bloody purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.24,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Use your power to bring the \Niron hammer of justice down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.00,main,,0,0,0,,upon those fiends in human skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.00,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,and restore this world to its proper state!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.85,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Bring their demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.87,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Bring about the great demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.46,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Please, Diablo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.22,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,This woman is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.14,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Please forgive my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:47.90,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,I will do everything I can \Nto investigate the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.10,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.77,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,I'm kind of beat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.61,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.41,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Diablo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.84,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,R-Rose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.79,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Are you awake, my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.76,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Replenishing your magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:16.99,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.29,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I can recover my magic power
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.26,main,Rose,0,0,0,,by staying in the dungeon or \Nstaying by your side, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.51,sign_14920_181_Charging,FlashingScreen,0,0,0,,{\pos(1554,165)\t(444,445,\alpha&FF&)\t(861,862,\alpha&00&)}<<Charging>>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:28.10,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Up until now, I've received magic power \Na bit at a time by staying near you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.97,sign_14920_181_Charging,FlashingScreen,0,0,0,,{\t(444,445,\alpha&FF&)\t(861,862,\alpha&00&)\an2\pos(870,165)}<<Charging>>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.43,sign_14920_181_Charging,FlashingScreen,0,0,0,,{\t(444,445,\alpha&FF&)\t(861,862,\alpha&00&)\an2\pos(1290,195)}<<Charging>>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.89,sign_14920_181_Charging,FlashingScreen,0,0,0,,{\t(442,443,\alpha&FF&)\t(859,860,\alpha&00&)\an2\pos(1605,51)}<<Charging>>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.77,main,Rose,0,0,0,,but I finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.81,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Beep, beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.07,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Charge is currently at 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.69,main,Rose,0,0,0,,We recommend switching to low-power mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.25,main,Rose,0,0,0,,...reached that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.24,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say something sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.40,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I didn't want to burden you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.91,main,Rose,0,0,0,,so every night, I waited \Nuntil after you went to bed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.43,main,Rose,0,0,0,,and quietly rested at your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.66,main,Rose,0,0,0,,but apparently I don't \Nrecharge when you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.80,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,You've been there this entire time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.22,main,Rose,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.22,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.91,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.18,main,Rose,0,0,0,,propose high-speed charging!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.14,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,"High-speed"? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:13.13,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Well, in just 30 minutes of action, I can \Nrecover a week's worth of Master's energy—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:17.11,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I mean, magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:20.07,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Okay, what do we need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.07,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:27.08,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I'll receive magic power through contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.66,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Contact? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.97,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,So where do we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.06,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Does the bed work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.92,main,Rose,0,0,0,,No, the bed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.48,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.92,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,I can't believe I just invited \Na woman to join me in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.59,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,And she shot me down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.76,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I'm heavy, so if I climbed into bed, it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.10,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,R-Right, her body is mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.10,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,All right. Tell me what \Nyou would like me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:53.06,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Th-Then if you'll pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.57,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Rose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.32,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:09.13,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Master, please charge me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.26,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Please bless me with your magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.79,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Rose, do you really need that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:21.21,main,Rose,0,0,0,,I don't have any experience either,\Nso I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:28.97,main,Rose,0,0,0,,B-But if I could have a part of your \Nbody make contact with my own, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.98,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,A p-part? Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.02,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,All right! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.44,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,S-So soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.36,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.61,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Where do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.95,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Here? Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.77,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Just do it the same way as when \NI poured magic power into Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.43,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go, Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.90,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:18.35,main,Rose,0,0,0,,My master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.71,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Rose, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.89,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Beep, beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.70,main,Rose,0,0,0,,Charge is currently at 120%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.75,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.54,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,All filled up now, Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.42,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.53,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Diablo-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.18,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,these are records of the Church's \Nfinancial dealings for these past few years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.89,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,and evidence of their various wrongdoings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.44,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,You gathered this much? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:01.86,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Well, I bought off the White Masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.32,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,The White Masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.20,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:10.70,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,They're the believers of great faith \Nwho are permitted to enter the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.85,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,You really bought off those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.21,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:20.17,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,When I told them I would buy evidence \Nof bribery, many of the White Masks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.39,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,According to these documents, \NVishos and those serving under him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:27.09,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,have been using a majority of the donations \Nfrom believers as their personal funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.73,main,Rem,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.80,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,That's not all, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.33,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Just as Vishos has tried \Nto kill Lumachina-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.83,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,he has killed many who \Ngot in their way already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.43,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Th-That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.64,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Unforgivable, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.73,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,God's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.38,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,God's own servants have \Ntaken the lives of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.61,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,And yet I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.28,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,I never knew about any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.16,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Lumachina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.08,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.62,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,I'm mad, I'm mad, I'm mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.59,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.34,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.08,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,The mortal races are disgusting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.23,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Ruin is the only path to their salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.06,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,This world needs a purge brought \Nabout by a Demon Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.44,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Now bring the bloody purge—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.54,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.85,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.27,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,But Diablo-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.73,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,even though we have all this evidence,\N the law cannot punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.73,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,We need your power to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.16,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Good grief... I guess it's come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.03,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Things might get a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.88,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Our turn's finally up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.75,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Facing the church, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.21,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Yeah! We can't let them do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.34,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Please wait, Diablo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:49.97,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Would you please grant \Nme just one more chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.34,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:56.43,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,I'm going to march to the Cathedral \Nwith this evidence in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.47,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,confront Vishos and his subordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.85,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,and pronounce their excommunication.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.61,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,She still insists on punishing \Nthem through proper means, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.73,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,That's just the kind of woman she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.50,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Diablo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.49,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Very well. You can give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.45,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Head Priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.71,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,this is as far as I can go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.29,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Please allow me to ask one last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.92,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,Do you believe the mortal \Nraces are worth saving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.96,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,That is for God to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:39.31,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,But it makes me happy when people are \Nable to live with a sense of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.53,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:46.10,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,The church is six blocks away from the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.05,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,These are the outfits worn by believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:54.30,main,Alicia,0,0,0,,If you wear them, you should be able to \Nget close to the sanctuary without trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.14,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Once we cross this bridge, \Nwe'll be in the church's district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.94,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,While there's no roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:05.22,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,it's as holy a place as the \Ninside of the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.13,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Those who live here, and those who work here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.29,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,are all ardent believers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.08,main,Shera,0,0,0,,That's the cathedral?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.32,main,Horn,0,0,0,,It's more lackluster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.01,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.47,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,No, look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:25.06,main,Three,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.82,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Th-That's the sanctuary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.23,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I-It's floating! It's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.77,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Vishos and his subordinates are \Nup there in the sky, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.99,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,How do we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.79,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,We'll use the floating passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.74,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but are you pilgrims?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.63,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Please, allow me to offer you some prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.25,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.36,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:48.75,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,You're turning down prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.95,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.36,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,I responded like he was one of those \Nmarketers outside a train station!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.14,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Please forgive our rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:04.39,main,Rem,0,0,0,,We've just traveled here from \Nthe old Demon Lord's Domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.89,main,Rem,0,0,0,,We're just so eager, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.90,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,That's quite the long journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.12,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.08,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Let us offer prayers to \Nthese faithful believers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:14.44,main,,0,0,0,,who have visited from the \Nold Demon Lord's Domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.99,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,and build our faith together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.26,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.46,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Diablo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:26.12,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,To the faithful, prayers are \Nas important as breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.04,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:31.54,main,Believers,0,0,0,,God, grant these people your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:31.54,top,Believers,0,0,0,,Let your love and mercy be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.44,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Well, now I'm stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.35,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Vishos...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.84,main,Believer,0,0,0,,Vishos-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.18,main,Believer,0,0,0,,It's Vishos-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.20,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Vishos-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.91,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.03,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.04,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Head Priest Lumachina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.15,main,Sanro,0,0,0,,Th-This woman's the Head Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.16,main,Believer,0,0,0,,The Head Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.12,main,Believer,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.26,main,Believer,0,0,0,,What a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.49,main,Believer,0,0,0,,The Head Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:32.10,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Vishos, someone tried to kill me \Nwhen I went to Zircon Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.52,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.98,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,That man was the Paladin, Gewalt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:41.70,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,and Vishos, that assassin was sent by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.70,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,And now, in the carriage behind me,\N I've gathered evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:52.50,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,that all of you have killed many others, \Nalong with financial records of your bribery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.89,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,So I hereby pronounce:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:59.96,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Head Cardinal Vishos and those \NCardinals serving under him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.30,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,are hereby excommunicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.61,main,Believer,0,0,0,,E-Excommunicated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:06.80,main,Believer,0,0,0,,Vishos-sama is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.88,main,Believer,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.03,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.04,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,How deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:17.12,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,It would seem the duties of \NHead Priest were too much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.07,main,,0,0,0,,for a young, growing woman who wants to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.59,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,After abandoning your duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.64,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,engaging in all manner of debauchery,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:28.09,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,and returning with such \Nshady individuals in tow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:32.79,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,you've created such fake evidence \Nto attempt to cast us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.24,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.83,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,You would call my claims lies and falsehoods?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:38.04,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Your wrongdoing—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:41.26,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,There's no way such things could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.79,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,If those things were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.71,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,the church would lose all significance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:51.52,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,and the faith built up by our believers \Nwould lose all meaning, would it not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:58.02,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,No matter how great the cost, you must \Nrepent for the sins you've committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:02.74,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Absolutely right, Head Priest—\Nno, former Head Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:08.32,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,You've abandoned your duties \Nand hidden your whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:14.12,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Now you seek to destroy the very church \Nitself to cover your sloth and debauchery!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.13,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,H-How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.60,main,Shera,0,0,0,,R-Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:21.63,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't like where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.76,main,Rem,0,0,0,,Diablo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.76,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Lumachina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.76,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,If you get emotional now, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.51,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.37,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:32.30,italics,Diablo,0,0,0,,Don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.10,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Lumachina Weselia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.92,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,You should resign from your \Nposition as Head Priest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.45,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,and repent for your sin \Nof abandoning your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:50.03,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.39,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.70,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Seize this sinner and her companions!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.68,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Th-Th-There are so many Paladins!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.51,main,Horn,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:14.47,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,My believers, this is a great act of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:17.83,main,Vishos,0,0,0,,Now, seize those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.52,main,Rem,0,0,0,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:25.95,main,Shera,0,0,0,,Diablo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.49,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.43,main,Horn,0,0,0,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:39.02,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,I don't want to, but I guess\N I'll mow them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:39.94,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:42.12,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,You lost the debate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.88,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,That only leaves fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:51.64,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Even so, we can't allow blood \Nto be spilled at the cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.57,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:59.39,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,If it will save everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:01.64,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,You would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.83,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Then at least go on your own two feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:08.98,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,Lightning Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:17.37,main,Diablo,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die, \Nthen make way for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.13,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Thank you for the prayers \Nyou offered earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.54,main,Lumachina,0,0,0,,May God's blessings be upon all of you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:53.16,top,Vishos,0,0,0,,Soon even God will be within my grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:24:01.00,sign_34325_420_Next_Episode__He,Screen,0,0,0,,{\pos(1365,900)\fad(487,1)\fscx75}Next Episode    {\c&H4D1FAF&}"Storm the Church"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.64,top,Diablo,0,0,0,,I'll dole out punishment to those \Nof you who have lost faith in God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:58.44,top,Diablo,0,0,0,,All of you can face the same death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.00,top,Lumachina,0,0,0,,Diablo-sama, grant us judgment for our sins.
